*1月1日，
**蒙大拿州成为美国第13个将休闲用大麻合法化的州份<ref>[https://www.greatfallstribune.com/story/news/2020/12/30/montana-law-take-effect-residents-can-grow-possess-pot/4086023001/ Montana law to take effect; residents can grow, possess pot] {{Wayback|url=https://www.greatfallstribune.com/story/news/2020/12/30/montana-law-take-effect-residents-can-grow-possess-pot/4086023001/ |date=20210114215915 }} ''Great Falls Tribune'', December 30, 2020</ref>。
**[[2019冠状病毒病美国疫情|2019冠状病毒病病例数]]突破2000万<ref>[https://www.cbsnews.com/news/us-surpasses-20-million-cases-of-coronavirus-on-first-day-of-2021/ U.S. surpasses 20 million cases of coronavirus on first day of 2021] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/us-surpasses-20-million-cases-of-coronavirus-on-first-day-of-2021/ |date=20210101225013 }} CBS News, January 1, 2021</ref>。
