**在点票过程中，参议员[[泰德·克鲁兹|泰德·克鲁兹]]和[[美国众议院|众议员]][[保羅·戈薩拉|保羅·戈薩拉]]否决了亚利桑那州的点票结果，是自2004年众议员{{tsl|en|Stephanie Tubbs Jones|斯蒂芬妮·塔布斯·琼斯}}和参议员[[芭芭拉·柏克瑟|芭芭拉·柏克瑟]]反对[[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]在俄亥俄州击败[[約翰·福布斯·凱瑞|約翰·福布斯·凱瑞]]的结果以来，选举人团点票结果首次因有議員提出反對而需要進行表決<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nationalreview.com/corner/cruz-and-gosar-object-to-arizonas-electoral-votes/|title=Cruz and Gosar Object to Arizona’s Electoral Votes|date=2021-01-06|accessdate=2021-01-08|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123175804/https://www.nationalreview.com/corner/cruz-and-gosar-object-to-arizonas-electoral-votes/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ktvz.com/politics/2021/01/06/gop-challenges-arizona-electoral-votes-the-first-of-several-expected-objections-to-bidens-2020-win/|title=GOP challenges Arizona electoral votes, the first of several expected objections to Biden's 2020 win|date=2021-01-06|accessdate=2021-01-08|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123173950/https://ktvz.com/politics/2021/01/06/gop-challenges-arizona-electoral-votes-the-first-of-several-expected-objections-to-bidens-2020-win/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。结果确认后，特朗普承诺“有序移交”权力给拜登<ref>[https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/07/trump-says-there-will-be-an-orderly-transition-of-power.html -{Trump now promises an ‘orderly transition’ of power after Congress confirms Biden win}- ] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/07/trump-says-there-will-be-an-orderly-transition-of-power.html |date=20210123174040 }} CNBC, January 7, 2021</ref>。
